roles.char: Twice Divorced Lady checking Frank out.

title: Episode #1.1668
description: Faith apologizes to Sgt. Speed. Ari visits Faith twice and meets Jill at Spencer's. He shows Jill the stella of Merit Kara that looks like Faith in profile. Barbara Wilde serves the lawsuit on the Hospital and its staff. Roger and Seneca plan their strategy. Roger meets EJ and they visit Rae. Faith wears a black dress with a large golden necklace for her date with Ari. Sgt Speed asks to be assigned to Ari.

title: Episode #1.1669
description: Faith in her black sort of egyptian dress finishes her date with Ari as Jill arrives. Jill tells Faith that she is frightened for her since Ari is very obsessed with the Merit Kara. Jack tells Joe that Perry wants to see him. Joe feels that he has done enough for the Feds. Roger, EJ and Rae continue their party. When EJ leaves Rae warns him off of EJ. Roger has a big brother talk with Faith. Rae tries to gets EJ a job at Barbara's soap. Joe meets with Perry.

title: Episode #1.1670
description: Ari gets Faith to pose for Ari's stella. EJ goes to the Soap's office to get a job. She is the right size for the nurse's uniform so she gets to act as Barbara's nurse. EJ misses her mark while wheeling Barbara in thus provoking an argument on the set. Faith and Ari go to Spencer's house for the photo session. Faith again looks just like the Merit Kara. Spencer sees them. The curse of the Merit Kara strikes.

title: Episode #1.1671
description: Faith,Jill,Mendenhall,Spencer's doctor,and Ari discuss what happened to Spencer. They decide to continue Spencer's work. Rae is surprised that EJ is an actress. They hope to catch Barbara faking her injury. Maeve warns Roger to go slowly with EJ. Delia agrees to go with Little John on a school trip. Delia shows even more acting talent when she barges in on Roger and EJ's dinner complaining of her arm injury.

title: Episode #1.1672
description: Wes barges into Rae's office and describes to EJ his latest story. Delia complains to Joe about how pushy EJ is. At Barbara's soap EJ tries to sweet talk Barbara and Henry but at one point Barbara tells Ej that EJ is not an actress. Delia tells Joe that she is still interested in Roger. Joe tells her to go for it. Joe buys an Egyptian statue and calls Ari to sell it to him.

title: Episode #1.1673
description: In Ryan's Bar Johnny asks Jill to say when Little John could call Frank. Jill then explains to Jack about the curse of the Merit Kara. Jack smells a story and goes with Jill to meet Ari and Faith. Ari strongly objects to Jill revealing the secrets of the Merit Kara to a reporter. At the police academy Sgt. Speed nitpicks Siobhan's grammar. Joe talks to Father Emmerich

title: Episode #1.1675
description: Ari is upset that Spencer did not reveal the location of the Shrine of Merit Kara and that Jill talked to a reporter. Faith assures him about Jack's ethics. Joe sells the statue to Ari. EJ and Delia chat with Maeve while Maeve peels carrots. EJ has dinner with Roger. Delia sends them a singing telegram. EJ charms Roger with her former career as an auto mechanic.

title: Episode #1.1676
description: Jill tells Ari about Joe. Jonas Rovings wants to catalog Spencer's collection but Jill and Ari want to find the shrine first. EJ gives storyline advice to Barbara and the Soap's Producer. Seneca tries to delay Barbara's lawsuit. Ari interrupts Faith while she catches up with Sgt Speed.

title: Episode #1.1677
description: On the set of Barbara's Soap Seneca looks on as the cast is called to the set. Ej avoids Seneca by going to a phone booth. Joe looks at Siobhan's photo and has a flashback which Delia interrupts. Delia is unhappy wit a new female employee and is sorry for Joe. Jack and Siobhan meet with Little John and Ryan to make a Christmas gift list. EJ has Seneca paged away from the set. Jack goes to Joe and tells him to forget Siobhan. EJ places Barbara's copy of the script on a high shelf but Barbara uses a mechanical device to grab it. Their cat and mouse game will continue. The end credits appear over a shot of the boom mike.

title: Episode #1.1678
description: In Ryan's Bar Kevin talks about Karl Marx while making 20 cent Irish Coffees. Faith comes in with Ari and introduces him to the Ryans. At Spencer's Jonas and Jill discuss the planned museum. In Seneca's office Seneca and Roger discuss Barbara's case. Roger believes that Barbara is faking and tells Seneca that Barbara is a resourceful actress that researches her roles and that she has had many occasions to study medical problems. Later Rae barges in on Roger while he is doing sit-ups. Rae seems impressed with Roger's shoulder muscles and tells him about her ambitions for EJ. Faith tells Ari about her teenage adventures. Jonas asks Mendenhall if there are any other storage areas that Jonas hasn't seen.

title: Episode #1.1679
description: In Rae's office Rae and EJ discuss the case and then Rae noticing EJ's lack of sleep sends her home. Naturally the Ryan Family watches Barbara's Soap and spot EJ in it. EJ covers somewhat by leaving out exactly what her Soap story is about. Joe keeps Orson on retainer but kicks him out of the Crystal Palace. Ari buys the statue from Joe.

title: Episode #1.1680
description: At Faith's on the phone she invites herself over to Ari's hotel room. Ari is very impatient that he is so close to the Merit Kara but can't get at it. Rae and EJ talk about reporting then EJ meets Barbara in her dressing room. EJ tries to sweet talk Barbara but Barbara becomes more suspicious. Rae barges into Maeve's kitchen and tells Maeve to leave her young reporter alone.

title: Episode #1.1681
description: In Ari's hotel room Faith looks in a mirror while touching her cross. Ari appears behind her and he nuzzles her neck. Faith sees a hand opening the door and yells out. Whoever it is escapes. Ari and Faith go to Jill's office to complain about Jill blabbing to reporters. At Barbara's soap EJ tries to nick Barbara's keys while Barbara prepares for an interview with photos. At the Crystal Palace Jack and Bob talk with George Cooney. Later Jack and Joe trade insults. Sgt Speed comes in later to see Joe. Faith invites Ari to the beach house.

title: Episode #1.1682
description: The beach house is very cold so Faith and Ari take a walk. A dark figure plants bugs while they are gone. Roger and Johnny watch Barbara's Soap while Delia complains about EJ's duplicity. In her excitement she gives Roger a good view of her slip. Roger remembers a date with EJ, however, and departs. When EJ arrives they have a nasty fight. Later a talk with Joe revives Delia's spirits. At the beach house Faith gets cozy with Ari then notices signs of an intruder.

title: Episode #1.1687
description: At Spencer's old place Jonas discusses the inventory with Ari at gunpoint. Later Ari complains to Jill about Jonas. Jill stresses the importance of following Spencer's wishes. At the Crystal Palace Joe greets Roger and then Delia tries to flirt with him. During the conversation Delia regrets sending that nasty letter to Barbara so she goes to studio to intercept it but the episode ends with Barbara's reading a letter. Barbara has a classic cat swallowed the canary look on her face

title: Episode #1.1688
description: At Spencer's old place Jonas discusses Ari with Jill about Jonas. Ari discovers that his hotel room is bugged. Barbara shows Delia's letter to the producer who says that he will handle it. Ari tells Faith about the bug. While holding Faith in his arms he explains the importance of finding the Merit Kara.

roles.char: Delia Reid Ryan Ryan Coleridge Crane
